{"tid":1609214,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中學生遭港警槍擊命危      台灣總統府：表達強烈遺憾      動用國家暴力只會惡化情勢","createTime":"2019-10-01T13:57:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T23:43:43.000Z","uid":35790,"like":275,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":66,"replies":[{"pid":"1290ade219eacb729e728fb02806a443053af78b","tid":1609214,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T13:57:56.000Z","msg":"中學生遭港警槍擊命危 總統府：動用國家暴力只會惡化情勢<br />\n<br />\n2019-10-01 <br />\n<br />\n〔記者蘇永耀／台北報導〕香港反送中運動今天下午爆發警察近距離開槍射擊年輕黑衣示威者的流血事件，<span style=\"color: red;\">總統府指出，針對稍早媒體報導香港反送中運動爆發激烈衝突，甚至有參與抗爭的中學生遭港府執法人員開槍致重傷，我們表達強烈遺憾。</span><br />\n<br />\n總統府強調，事實證明，對渴望民主的人民動用國家暴力，只會讓情勢不斷惡化，最終導致悲劇的發生。我們呼籲香港政府當局，停止鎮壓手段，儘速並誠意開啟社會對話，落實對港人自由民主的嚴肅承諾，以化解不必要的衝突。<br />\n<br />\n香港反送中運動今天爆發警察近距離開槍射擊年輕黑衣示威者的流血事件，開槍距離不足1公尺，中槍的中學生目前危殆。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/news.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/politics/breakingnews/2933196\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Famp%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2933196&d=JxnAwUrH%2B1qYxVTFfur%2BVnGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=07b94a15\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/news.ltn.com.tw/amp/news/politics/breakingnews/2933196</a>"},{"pid":"f23961c58bdc1f539cccf3b818cf1aac43200df1","tid":1609214,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T13:58:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceb4b47ce241a5bdc0eb733cc2d4dbfc9e7f8a3f","tid":1609214,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T13:58:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3390585e1b02ed3dd894cfe4f4a7039b11ad8dcc","tid":1609214,"uid":149494,"like":68,"dislike":0,"score":68,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T13:59:08.000Z","msg":"美國、台灣、香港<br />